testcase.name: Electron host configuration › enforces preload hardening and IPC allowlist
Electron host configuration › preload exposes repo health API and devDocs allowlist
Electron host configuration › preload repoHealth enforces config-only gate and output readability
Repo health server logic › returns healthy when required and optional artifacts exist
Repo health server logic › reports missing required artifact for unhealthy repo
Repo health server logic › blocks repo outside allowlist
Repo health server logic › fails when output folder is configured but missing
Repo health server logic › passes when only config exists and no output folder configured
Repo health server logic › persists, reads, and clears active repo record
Story 1.1 — Repo selection, validation, and persistence (config gate) › [P0] validates healthy repo when config exists and persists active+recent state
Story 1.1 — Repo selection, validation, and persistence (config gate) › [P0] restore revalidates and clears active on unhealthy repo
Story 1.1 — Repo selection, validation, and persistence (config gate) › [P1] fails when output folder configured but unreadable
Story 1.1 — Repo selection, validation, and persistence (config gate) › [P1] rejects repos outside allowlist
Story 1.1 — Repo selection, validation, and persistence (config gate) › [P1] restore returns persisted repo state and artifacts
Story 1.1 — Repository store API contracts › revalidates saved repo on launch and returns health status
Story 1.1 — Repository store API contracts › rejects invalid repos and surfaces missing artifacts on persist
